video.title: Paparazzi footage of champion boxer Roy Jones Jr. at Good Morning America in New York City
video.description: Boxer Roy Jones Jr. arrives to ABC Studios for a guest appearance on 'Good Morning America' in New York City, to promote his November 8th boxing match at Madison Square Garden. At almost 40 years of age, Roy is near the end of his career. He stops to sign autographs for some fans and they wish him good luck with the fight. One fan also yells that he "better eat those wheaties!"
